{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"U556STORY2","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["A Knight's Promise\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2 - Are You Busy, Commander?<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","say":"After a bit of a hectic start, we finally got the day back on track.","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"At first, U-556 needed a lot of guidance in performing her secretarial duties. But by mid morning she knew what she was doing and was ready to help with a workload a bit heavier than usual.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hmmhmmhmmm♪～","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":408040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"She was engrossed in reading some After Action Reports. I decided to let her focus on her work.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Fifteen minutes later...","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":30,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.4,"y":0}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Ugh, I'm so bored! I thought being secretary ship would be easy and fun. I thought I'd just be playing with the Commander all the time...","actor":408040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Tactfully decline her offer."}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.2,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"Heyyyy, Commanderrr! How about we knock off work and go play for a while!","actor":408040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"Awwww!","actor":408040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"withoutActorName":true,"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"U-556 looked a little dejected.","actor":408040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"Is this work really that important?","actor":408040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"It seemed like U-556 fundamentally misunderstood the relationship between commander and secretary ship. To her, they were little more than playmates.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Still, the way she took to organizing the office and earnestly focused on her work from dawn until now was certainly praiseworthy... I decided to explain to her the meaning behind our efforts.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"Commander? What's wrong? Why do you suddenly look all serious...","actor":408040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]},"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"I get it now... Without you, the whole port wouldn't be able to function. The Commander's work is really more important than I ever thought...","actor":408040},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"That's why I gotta help out!","actor":408040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"U-556 seemed like she understood what we were doing. So I took advantage of her enthusiasm and gave her some simple things to work on.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"x":2500,"type":"move","delay":1,"dur":0.5,"y":0}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"Just hand this over to Akashi down at the shop? I'm on it!","actor":408040},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"U-556 snatched the document out of my hand and flew out the door.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"It turned out that with the right spirit, she'd be able to handle something like this.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"stopbgm":true,"say":"......","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"But by lunchtime, U-556 still hadn't come back.","blackBg":true,"dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}}]}